feat: end-to-end live demo on Vercel

Curio is now reachable at a single Vercel URL with the full Tollgate-402
flow working in simulated payment mode:
  - 402 challenge from /api/examples/api/* (paywall middleware)
  - intent created via /api/v1/intent
  - simulated webhook accepted at /api/v1/webhook/helius
  - JWT issued from /api/v1/confirm
  - paid retry returns mock data with citations

Three coordinated changes:

1) shared in-process store (apps/curio/lib/shared-store.ts) keeps the
   InMemoryStore on globalThis so warm Vercel invocations across the
   /api/v1/* and /api/examples/* handlers see the same state. Pre-seeds
   the 5 known endpoints synchronously on cold start so the very first
   /v1/intent works without waiting on examples to register.

2) HMAC bypass in webhook handler when TOLLGATE_SKIP_ONCHAIN_VERIFY=true
   (the existing dev/sim flag). Avoids leaking the webhook secret into
   the agent SDK for simulated payments.

3) examples-prefix stripping fix: /api/examples/api/news is rewritten
   to /api/news for the examples Hono app (was rewriting to /api/api/news).

README live-demo URL added.
